  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Key Features</strong></u> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Kanji Journey Begins</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with Hiragana and Katakana to build a solid foundation.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kanji Legends contains interactive tools for effective Kanji retention.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every Kanji is sorted into tiers and lists, ready to explore and learn at your own pace. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kanji Legends</strong> offers a list of over 2000 <strong>Jōyō Kanji.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Practice</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create <strong>custom challenges</strong> with your own selection of characters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn at your own pace in a calm and soothing environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train for the <strong>challenging trials</strong>, with no timers and rules!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/a15094217a86602887c6de60eaccf7a4.poster.avif?t=1751660272\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/a15094217a86602887c6de60eaccf7a4.webm?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/a15094217a86602887c6de60eaccf7a4.mp4?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenge</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on various <strong>challenges</strong> with both Kana and Kanji characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your knowledge with <strong>timed quizzes</strong> and  <strong>memory games</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a wide range of <strong>difficulties</strong> and rules. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy fun and engaging challenges—some with delightfully ridiculous settings and rules.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/522003b4eca02df03249ae5d31c753ad.poster.avif?t=1751660272\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/522003b4eca02df03249ae5d31c753ad.webm?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/522003b4eca02df03249ae5d31c753ad.mp4?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a vast selection of collectibles throughout the game.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Kanji Cards by completing specific challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/918637e70871547713cb221cc6990e19.poster.avif?t=1751660272\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/918637e70871547713cb221cc6990e19.webm?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/918637e70871547713cb221cc6990e19.mp4?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb the ranks</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each challenge comes with a specific rank level.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through the ranks by mastering each challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Become the <strong>Ultimate Master</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Key Features</strong></u> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Kanji Journey Begins</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with Hiragana and Katakana to build a solid foundation.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kanji Legends contains interactive tools for effective Kanji retention.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every Kanji is sorted into tiers and lists, ready to explore and learn at your own pace. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kanji Legends</strong> offers a list of over 2000 <strong>Jōyō Kanji.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Practice</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create <strong>custom challenges</strong> with your own selection of characters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn at your own pace in a calm and soothing environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train for the <strong>challenging trials</strong>, with no timers and rules!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/a15094217a86602887c6de60eaccf7a4.poster.avif?t=1751660272\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/a15094217a86602887c6de60eaccf7a4.webm?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/a15094217a86602887c6de60eaccf7a4.mp4?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenge</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on various <strong>challenges</strong> with both Kana and Kanji characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your knowledge with <strong>timed quizzes</strong> and  <strong>memory games</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a wide range of <strong>difficulties</strong> and rules. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy fun and engaging challenges—some with delightfully ridiculous settings and rules.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/522003b4eca02df03249ae5d31c753ad.poster.avif?t=1751660272\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/522003b4eca02df03249ae5d31c753ad.webm?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/522003b4eca02df03249ae5d31c753ad.mp4?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a vast selection of collectibles throughout the game.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Kanji Cards by completing specific challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/918637e70871547713cb221cc6990e19.poster.avif?t=1751660272\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/918637e70871547713cb221cc6990e19.webm?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124210/extras/918637e70871547713cb221cc6990e19.mp4?t=1751660272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb the ranks</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each challenge comes with a specific rank level.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through the ranks by mastering each challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Become the <strong>Ultimate Master</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
